\f0\fs26 \cf0 This game was my idea of bringing back some of the old console games with some of the new library improvements. This game features single player (infinite number of levels), local multiplayer (best over ssh) and online multiplayer head to head. It pretty much requires (on my 1280x800 monitor) that terminal be either fullscreen or fully maximized. This will be a fun experience for anybody who plays it. If you want, you can look at http://student.eup.k12.mi.us/~ss14bouchaj/MUD at some of the older copies I wrote when I was a little less organized at programming (if sks4200 segfaults it is because you went off the map or the program thought you did). Good luck, I would love to hear any feedback you have for me. To get ahold of me either email me (phyrrus9@gmail.com) or shoot me a tweet at @phyrrus9. Thank you and good luck!}
